<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00374/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<strong>项目描述：</strong>一件男士休闲衬衫。<br />
<span style="color: #bb0000">A.展开更多</span> <span style="color: #bb0000">B.展开更多</span>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">C.展开更多</a></div>
