<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/i-am-guao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5948673); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5948673&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160418" alt="I am GuAo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5948673)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/i-am-guao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5948673); return false;">I am GuAo</a></span></p>
