<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6441401&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160419" alt="zeta-9-beta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6441401)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zeta-9-beta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6441401); return false;">zeta-9-beta</a></span></p>
